    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 guidance for a Class II device with medium model influence. Validation results demonstrate NIH predictions within 8.7% RMS of experimental data across the full COU operating envelope. UQ campaign results documented in VR-02 confirm robustness of worst-case operating condition identification. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis conditions for the CPB device.",
